1
00:00:00,390 --> 00:00:04,914
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,914 --> 00:00:10,418
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,418 --> 00:00:16,846
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,846 --> 00:00:21,326
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,326 --> 00:00:25,774
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,774 --> 00:00:30,685
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,685 --> 00:00:34,734
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,734 --> 00:00:39,269
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,269 --> 00:00:43,566
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,566 --> 00:00:48,331
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,331 --> 00:00:51,822
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,822 --> 00:00:55,502
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,148 --> 00:01:00,526
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,526 --> 00:01:03,214
=Episode 12=

15
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:20,000
Let's leave.

16
00:01:22,933 --> 00:01:24,899
Stop it.

17
00:01:39,066 --> 00:01:42,033
Why did you help me today?

18
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:48,533
I heard you had a crush on me
for a long time, asking around about me.

19
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,900
Alright, thanks.

20
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:53,366
But how did you know I was there?

21
00:01:54,333 --> 00:01:55,133
Well...

22
00:01:55,566 --> 00:01:58,766
I saw you leaving the company today,
looking suspicious,

23
00:01:59,866 --> 00:02:00,766
so I followed you.

24
00:02:01,533 --> 00:02:02,533
Are you that bored?

25
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:05,400
My Muay Thai gym is near your company.

26
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,266
So you run that gym.

27
00:02:07,266 --> 00:02:07,666
Cool?

28
00:02:07,666 --> 00:02:08,766
No wonder it's empty.

29
00:02:08,766 --> 00:02:09,500
Shush.

30
00:02:12,566 --> 00:02:13,500
Give me some face.

31
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:19,100
So I'm taking on some odd jobs now
to sustain the gym operation.

32
00:02:22,933 --> 00:02:23,733
You can come.

33
00:02:26,933 --> 00:02:27,933
Master of Muay Thai.

34
00:02:28,733 --> 00:02:31,833
(Part-time Services)
Post-production editing, boxing company.

35
00:02:32,333 --> 00:02:33,600
What a wide variety.

36
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,933
I'm capable, right?

37
00:02:35,433 --> 00:02:36,233
Alright.

38
00:02:36,766 --> 00:02:38,133
Miss Jin, please wait.

39
00:02:43,633 --> 00:02:46,333
Do you believe in love at first sight?

40
00:02:49,566 --> 00:02:52,100
Ever since you hit me, I've found...

41
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,033
It's chaotic enough.

42
00:02:57,533 --> 00:02:58,566
You're ridiculous.

43
00:03:10,833 --> 00:03:12,033
Why are there so many reporters?

44
00:03:12,666 --> 00:03:16,833
Everyone, go back first.
Don't disturb the neighbors.

45
00:03:18,366 --> 00:03:19,366
You want to go near?

46
00:03:19,433 --> 00:03:20,800
Don't you know?

47
00:03:23,733 --> 00:03:26,333
(Executives of WE Group were attacked)

48
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,133
(by Lan Chen's man in a bar.)

49
00:03:28,566 --> 00:03:30,033
(The group's financing failed.)

50
00:03:30,133 --> 00:03:32,833
(Mr. Lan had his secretary
threaten the CFO by force)

51
00:03:32,966 --> 00:03:36,066
(to keep the cooking secret,
but he blew the whistle instead.)

52
00:03:36,066 --> 00:03:37,800
I'll drive them away. Stay here.

53
00:03:42,466 --> 00:03:46,333
Please go back first.
Don't disturb the neighbors' rest.

54
00:03:47,933 --> 00:03:49,566
Disperse. Everyone, disperse.

55
00:03:50,433 --> 00:03:51,333
Why are you here?

56
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,333
Who are you?

57
00:03:58,548 --> 00:04:00,633
Mom.

58
00:04:00,633 --> 00:04:01,766
Take her to the hospital.

59
00:04:01,766 --> 00:04:02,466
Stop, stop.

60
00:04:02,466 --> 00:04:04,866
What's wrong? Miss Jin, come with me.

61
00:04:04,866 --> 00:04:07,500
Mr. Lan sent me over.
He's already dealing with this.

62
00:04:07,666 --> 00:04:09,166
Go. I'll be right there.

63
00:04:09,166 --> 00:04:09,966
Wait.

64
00:04:13,666 --> 00:04:16,933
I'm the boss of a Muay Thai gym.
Give me some respect.

65
00:04:27,533 --> 00:04:29,133
Didn't you go with that man?

66
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,200
No time to explain. Let's go.

67
00:04:35,233 --> 00:04:38,166
I-I-I haven't got on yet. Allow me.

68
00:04:46,666 --> 00:04:48,300
That's how it is.

69
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,800
Oh.

70
00:04:52,433 --> 00:04:54,233
The situation is a bit complicated.

71
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,966
I need some time.

72
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,600
So

73
00:04:58,833 --> 00:05:00,133
you hit me that day?

74
00:05:01,066 --> 00:05:02,600
No, it was you who hit me.

75
00:05:10,933 --> 00:05:12,533
She hit me. I-I-It was her.

76
00:05:13,633 --> 00:05:15,800
You're gentle. How could you...?

77
00:05:16,733 --> 00:05:19,800
So what now?

78
00:05:20,233 --> 00:05:22,200
Who just took you to the hospital?

79
00:05:22,733 --> 00:05:25,300
It was Mr. Li,
the general manager of the group.

80
00:05:26,466 --> 00:05:27,733
I'll check on Mom.

81
00:05:34,833 --> 00:05:36,000
Mr. Li left, right?

82
00:05:36,833 --> 00:05:37,766
I think so.

83
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:50,500
Don't hit me.

84
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,566
(Do you remember
what we talked about on the phone?)

85
00:06:01,566 --> 00:06:02,533
(WE Beauty Family)
(What?)

86
00:06:02,533 --> 00:06:04,833
(Did you find that strange report?)

87
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:08,933
(I reported it to the CFO a few times,
but he had no feedback.)

88
00:06:09,366 --> 00:06:13,133
(So I kept the file
in a pink folder on the file shelf)

89
00:06:13,333 --> 00:06:17,966
(in the President's office
at WE Beauty Family.)

90
00:06:19,833 --> 00:06:20,633
I found it.

91
00:06:22,566 --> 00:06:23,533
Why is it empty?

92
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:26,033
Where is it?

93
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:39,700
Chen,

94
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:44,533
this is how you manage the group?
You've lost all face for our family.

95
00:06:45,633 --> 00:06:49,000
We must resolve
this PR crisis immediately.

96
00:06:49,633 --> 00:06:51,566
Hold a news conference
tomorrow morning.

97
00:06:52,066 --> 00:06:56,133
You must answer to the group
and the public at the conference.

98
00:06:57,166 --> 00:06:59,500
Since the photo was taken by reporters,

99
00:06:59,966 --> 00:07:02,533
Miss Jin must be involved.

100
00:07:02,933 --> 00:07:04,700
To protect our reputation,

101
00:07:05,466 --> 00:07:07,933
we need to distance ourselves from her.

102
00:07:08,866 --> 00:07:11,200
Shufen, draft a statement.

103
00:07:11,433 --> 00:07:14,733
Tell the public
that it is Miss Jin's personal action.

104
00:07:15,066 --> 00:07:17,800
She is a temp and has nothing
to do with our group.

105
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:21,200
Fire her and reserve the right
to seek her liability.

106
00:07:21,866 --> 00:07:24,733
Aren't we going too far?

107
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,566
Although the girl comes
from a modest background

108
00:07:29,233 --> 00:07:32,100
and isn't well-educated,

109
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:35,433
we don't need to frame
such a young girl.

110
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:38,366
Her life would be ruined.

111
00:07:38,666 --> 00:07:39,933
Don't tell me what to do.

112
00:07:41,233 --> 00:07:42,766
It's about the group's image.

113
00:07:42,766 --> 00:07:44,733
And at this critical moment,

114
00:07:44,933 --> 00:07:46,866
such a hiccup happened.

115
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:50,033
Compassion will ruin things
sooner or later.

116
00:07:50,100 --> 00:07:51,433
I will do it, Grandfather.

117
00:07:52,733 --> 00:07:58,299
That's good.

118
00:07:58,399 --> 00:08:00,566
A man should prioritize the big picture.

119
00:08:01,266 --> 00:08:04,800
It's a few hours before the conference.
Go and prepare.

120
00:08:35,471 --> 00:08:45,295
(Miss Jin, you've worked hard. You will
have the day off tomorrow.)

121
00:08:47,857 --> 00:08:52,379
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

122
00:08:55,409 --> 00:09:00,370
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

123
00:09:03,419 --> 00:09:09,243
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

124
00:09:09,243 --> 00:09:16,713
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

125
00:09:16,713 --> 00:09:20,194
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

126
00:09:20,194 --> 00:09:24,315
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

127
00:09:24,315 --> 00:09:26,011
♪Open my secret♪

128
00:09:26,011 --> 00:09:32,059
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

129
00:09:32,059 --> 00:09:35,931
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

130
00:09:35,931 --> 00:09:40,437
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

131
00:09:40,437 --> 00:09:49,147
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
